Catherine is 13 years old and in form one. She has four siblings and stays in Kibera five km away. She treks to and from school every morning and evening. Her mother is the only parent, but is unemployed. Catherine was in and out of school during her first term in form one until she came to St. Mathews in the second term of 2011. She is now settled and working hard. She is a determined girl, disciplined and well focused. She needs great financial assistance and with that she has a great future. 
